    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed at MRL 5 achieved levels meeting or exceeding required levels. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification confirms 95th-percentile hemolysis index predictions remain below the absolute clinical threshold across all 5 COU operating points. Independent review completed. The ContextOfUse description enumerates the intended operating ranges in detail (temperature, pressure, flow rate, impeller speed, fluid properties), providing the reader with apparent coverage of the clinical envelope. The credibility assessment is accepted for regulatory submission.",
